        - #58 Fix missing portal type in query
        - #57 Fix search catalog for metadata lookup
        - #56 Fix implicit imports for controlpanel mappings
        - #54 Lookup mapped catalogs for CatalogBrains
        
        
        2.4.0 (2023-03-10)
        ------------------
        
